</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Cadillac Fairview, the North American property group which is restructuring
its CDollars 5bn (USDollars 3.6bn) debt, has sold its half-interest in three
Canadian shopping malls to the Ontario Teachers' Pension Plan Board for
