<HEADLINE>
FT  03 JUN 94 / UK Company News: Wyndeham Press advances to Pounds 1.76m
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Wyndeham Press Group, the printing and packaging company, reported pre-tax
profits up from Pounds 1.02m to Pounds 1.76m for the year to end-March.
Turnover, boosted by Pounds 2.95m from acquisitions, was up from Pounds
10.6m to Pounds 13.5m.
Earnings per share emerged at 7.1p (4.6p) and a final dividend of 1.5p is
proposed, making 2.25p (1.25p) for the year.
