FT  03 JUN 94 / Letters to the Editor: Supporters of Chalfont and others
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
   From Ms KAY COLEMAN and Others
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
Sir, To Lord Chalfont and others (Letters, May 31), hear] hear] - and so say
all of us not so silent chief executives.
Kay Coleman, Marianne Dobkin, Dawn Gibbons, Jackie Edelson, Sarah Topham,
Janet Larton, Evy Blaskey.
(all signatories are chief executives or managing directors of companies in
the north-west)
